Hey ! what’s up food hunters 😎? Wanna eat like a Hongkie(local people)? Let us take u to some Bargaining 💰💰Restaurants for great foods 🥣 ,i went in this place for lunch, i have order 2lunch sets a spring onions pork chop with rice and a tomato & cream sauce pork chop baked rice both set comes with a drink , the spring onion pork chop rice is good strong spring onions taste and smell , the baked pork chop rice is about average i will say the spring onions pork chop is a better choice then the baked pork chop rice , there is no queue when i get here at 14:00 on weekend , i spend about HK$90 for the lunch sets average HK$45 per head .

result.adr_address: 香港長沙灣元州街418號
result.name: 百份百餐廳

reviews.text: 😋Yummy

咖喱類比近李鄭屋果間，辣好多及冇咁香。

地方都寬敞好坐，服務不錯，價格適中唔算中上，只係午餐比一般茶餐廳，貴少許而已。

如果食下午茶餐，價格都好相宜，而且款式選擇多，值得去幫襯。
中上位價錢, 套餐有特色, 我這個迷你海南雞飯加碗仔翅套餐下午茶, $ 34元, 過得去啦! 只是飯是不暖的, 碗仔翅尚可. 最贊是杯即磨咖啡, 奶味綿滑, 濃郁適中。

採光度高,地方清潔。
價錢不過不失
味道合格,份量充足

可以一試

服務幾好可惜雲閃付有時得有時唔得，食完才唔得變食貴餐
1/6又一次雲閃額满，我還可相信你嗎?雲閃百分百
